# Wisp React

- Functional components; extract hooks for terminal, shortcuts, command history
- Tab state in Zustand (useTabStore); no prop drilling for tabs
- Compose shadcn primitives; add via CLI, don't hand-copy component source
- DropdownMenuItem inside DropdownMenuGroup; Button icons use data-icon
- PTY/xterm lifecycle in useTerminal hook; keep components presentational
